            <!-- ======== SHORT BIO ======== -->
            <h2><font face="Arial" color="#003322">A Little About Me</font></h2>

            <p><font face="Arial" size="3">
              I am a <b>final-year Information Systems student</b> at UiTM Shah Alam,
              passionate about web technology, digital design, and problem solving.
              I enjoy building things from scratch &mdash; this website being one of them.
            </font></p>

            <blockquote>
              <p><font face="Arial" size="3">
                <q>The best way to learn web design is to actually build something &mdash;
                one tag at a time.</q>
              </font></p>
            </blockquote>

            <p><font face="Arial" size="3">
              Outside of studies, I enjoy <mark>reading</mark>, <mark>photography</mark>,
              and exploring new technology.
            </font></p>

            <br />


